title: NAS Oceana Airshow 2008 feat. US Navy Blue Angels
description:
This is raw video from the Naval Air Station Oceana Golden Anniversary Airshow on September 19-21, 2008.  Acts include:

US Air Force B52 Stratofortress (static)
US Air Force C17 Globemaster
US Marines C130 Hercules (Blue Angels "Fat Albert")
US Navy E2 Hawkeye
US Navy F/A18 Hornet
US Navy Blue Angels
US Air Force F22 Raptor
US Navy SNJ (Geico Skytypers)
L39 Albatros (takiing) 
Civilian performers Patty Wagstaff and Manfred Radius
USO Skydiving Team
Airshow Narrator Rob Reider
Crowd Reaction to Blue Angels Sneak Pass and the F22 Raptor

This video was shot from the crowdline with a Nikon Coolpix L1.  It is uncompressed Quicktime.

-----

Also included are my photos from the event.
